OL,3,CHow much are you paying for your
OL,4,Cchild's summer childcare?
OL,6,FParents needing childcare over the six-
OL,7,Fweek summer holidays will need to fork
OL,8,Fout #1,076 per child on average ` a
OL,9,Frise of 4% on last year, a report has
OL,10,Ffound.
OL,12,FCouncils across the country are facing
OL,13,Fshortages of holiday childcare spaces,
OL,14,Fespecially for children with special
OL,15,Feducational needs and disabilities
OL,16,F(Send), according to research by the
OL,17,FCoram Family and Childcare charity.
