OL,3,CHow much are you paying for your
OL,4,Cchild's summer childcare?
OL,6,FThe shortage has contributed to the
OL,7,Frising costs, with holiday childcare
OL,8,Fcosting almost #700 more over six
OL,9,Fweeks than term-time after-school
OL,10,Fclubs.
OL,12,FThe research, based on surveys of
OL,13,Flocal authorities in England, Scotland
OL,14,Fand Wales between April and June,
OL,15,Fsuggests the average cost of a holiday
OL,16,Fchildcare club has risen by 4% in a
OL,17,Fyear to #179 per week.
OL,19,FWales has the highest weekly price at
OL,20,F#210, followed by England at #178 and
OL,21,FScotland at #168.
