OL,6,FThere is significant variation in
OL,7,Fholiday club prices across England,
OL,8,Franging from #196 per week in the
OL,9,FSouth East to #162 per week in the
OL,10,FNorth West.
OL,12,FThe report also found that the average
OL,13,Fcost of a childminder during the
OL,14,Fholidays is #234 per week in the UK.
OL,16,FInner London has the highest
OL,17,Fchildminder price at #306 per week,
OL,18,Fcompared to the South West where the
OL,19,Fchildminder cost is #191 per week.
