OL,3,CHow much are you paying for your
OL,4,Cchild's summer childcare?
OL,6,FIn England, only 9% of local
OL,7,Fauthorities said they had enough
OL,8,Fholiday childcare for at least three
OL,9,Fquarters of children with Send in
OL,10,Ftheir area.
OL,12,FThis figure falls to 0% for three
OL,13,Fregions in England ` the East
OL,14,FMidlands, the East of England and
OL,15,FInner London, the report said.
OL,17,FThe charity is calling on the
OL,18,Fgovernment to provide more funding,
OL,19,Ftraining and support to holiday
OL,20,Fchildcare providers to meet the needs
OL,21,Fof Send children.
