OL,6,FThe holiday activities and food (HAF)
OL,7,Fprogramme - which funds local
OL,8,Fauthorities to provide holiday
OL,9,Fchildcare, activities and food for
OL,10,Fchildren eligible for free school
OL,11,Fmeals - should also be maintained
OL,12,Fafter March 2026 to ensure
OL,13,Fdisadvantaged children have childcare
OL,14,Fduring school holidays, it added.
