OL,3,CHow much are you paying for your
OL,4,Cchild's summer childcare?
OL,6,FThe expansion of funded childcare,
OL,7,Fwhich was introduced by the
OL,8,FConservative government, began being
OL,9,Frolled out in England in April last
OL,10,Fyear for working parents of two-year-
OL,11,Folds.
OL,13,FWorking parents of children older than
OL,14,Fnine months are now able to access 15
OL,15,Fhours of funded childcare a week
OL,16,Fduring term time, before the full
OL,17,Frollout of 30 hours a week to all
OL,18,Feligible families in September.
